<H1> 291 B.C.    Olympiad 122.2</H1>
<BR> Consuls: L. Postumius L.f. <A CLASS="help" HREF="../names/m/megellus.html#1">Megellus</A> (III), C. Junius C.f. <A CLASS="help" HREF="../names/b/bubulcus.html#2">Bubulcus</A> Brutus 
<BR>   Athenian <A CLASS="help" HREF="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Archon_of_Athens">archon</A>: Charinus
