<TR><TH VALIGN=TOP> <A NAME=8>8</A>
<TD> <FONT CLASS="green">ROM</FONT> <B> <A CLASS="help" HREF="../names/l/luscinus.html#1">Fabricius</A> supports <A CLASS="help" HREF="../names/r/rufinus.html#1">Rufinus,</A> his personal enemy, as a candidate for the consulship of 290 B.C.</B>
